<h1>Welcome to the Fitness Program Manager</h1>

<p>The <strong>Fitness Program Manager</strong> is a web application that allows you to manage fitness programs efficiently. Below are the key features of the application:</p>

<h2>Key Features</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Search for fitness programs by name.</li>
    <li>Sort programs by name, type, and difficulty level.</li>
    <li>Create, edit, and delete fitness programs.</li>
    <li>View detailed information about each fitness program.</li>
    <li>Rate fitness programs and view average ratings.</li>
</ul>

<p>Use the navigation menu at the top to access the list of fitness programs or to create a new one.</p>
